###Recommended workflow for a new Replit project:###

- Create a new Replit workspace (blank or from a template)
- Build your app with the agent first — get it working
- When you're ready to deploy, run setup:

   curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tmenna/deployment-template/main/scripts/deploy-setup.sh | bash

- Follow the prompts (hit Enter for detected defaults)
- Your app is live on Render
- For every update after that:

   bash scripts/deploy-push.sh "Describe what changed"

Key point: Build first, then deploy. 
The setup script is a one-time step at the end of your first working session, not something you run before building. 
After that, deploy-push.sh is all you need for any future changes.
